OL,3,CRail crossing closed after trespassers
OL,4,Ccaught lying down for selfies
OL,6,FA level crossing has been shut in an
OL,7,Femergency move after a string of
OL,8,F"truly shocking" incidents of
OL,9,Ftrespassing on the railway.
OL,11,FNetwork Rail recorded 15 incidents at
OL,12,FWilthorpe crossing, near Barnsley, in
OL,13,Fthe last two months.
OL,15,FIt has released CCTV footage showing
OL,16,Fyoung people holding the gates shut to
OL,17,Fstop others from leaving the track and
OL,18,Flaying down on the live line for
OL,19,Fphotographs.
