OL,3,CRail crossing closed after trespassers
OL,4,Ccaught lying down for selfies
OL,6,FOthers were seen crossing while a
OL,7,Ftrain was approaching. In another
OL,8,Fincident ballast was placed on the
OL,9,Ftrack.
OL,11,FLevel crossing manager Andy Cunningham
OL,12,Fsaid: "The footage from Wilthorpe is
OL,13,Ftruly shocking and the worst I've seen
OL,14,Ffor misuse and disregard for level
OL,15,Fcrossing safety."
OL,17,FHe said it was fortunate no-one had
OL,18,Fdied as the crossing has limited of
OL,19,Fapproaching trains.
