OL,3,CRail crossing closed after trespassers
OL,4,Ccaught lying down for selfies
OL,6,FNetwork Rail's application for a
OL,7,Fclosure was granted by Barnsley
OL,8,FCouncil on Thursday and will last for
OL,9,Fthree weeks.
OL,11,FMr Cunningham apologised for the
OL,12,Finconvenience, adding: "We are aware
OL,13,Fthat this is a popular walking route
OL,14,Ffor residents and our decision to seek
OL,15,Fthis emergency closure was not taken
OL,16,Flightly," he said.
