OL,6,F"But given the evidence and the
OL,7,Fseverity of the situation, we believe
OL,8,Fthat closing the crossing is the most
OL,9,Fresponsible course of action to
OL,10,Fprevent any potential accidents or
OL,11,Finjuries.
OL,13,FNetwork Rail is seeking a six-month
OL,14,Ftemporary traffic regulation order
OL,15,Fafter the three-week closure.
